{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cd25af777d","title":"邓小平就北京大学文化革命运动对女儿邓楠的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4ba576aa54","index":0,"year":1966,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"cd25af777d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"70f02a0dc7","name":"资产阶级反动路线","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"fb776baaf9","name":"邓小平","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8463c1566f","type":"title","text":"邓小平就北京大学文化革命运动对女儿邓楠的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"8093e133bc","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平就北京大学文化革命运动对女儿邓楠的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"5ab00d9d66","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"f7e26b4f49","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.06.22","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"708609bb1d","type":"paragraph","text":"1、放手发动群众，最后达到95％，打击面要小。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"0b48a4e185","type":"paragraph","text":"2、排队，给老师、同学、左、中、右都排队。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"0d7a6eeb0b","type":"paragraph","text":"3、不断地扩大左派队伍，争取中间派，批落后分子、右派队伍。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"5d76733e51","type":"paragraph","text":"4、工作队应该起个参谋作用，指出方向，出点子，想想办法，让学生自己去做。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"754a9582ca","type":"paragraph","text":"5、师生要挂勾，发动群众，让学生做老师的工作，让学生动动脑筋，培养学生分析问题研究问题的能力。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"54c38e5f8d","type":"paragraph","text":"6、要文斗，不要武斗，打人是最容易的事，……给坏人造成混乱时机。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"e60321980b","type":"paragraph","text":"7、不打无准备之仗，哪怕晚几天都行，目标一定要选中、选对，要给各种人排队分类，揪出主要矛盾。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"6551055da4","type":"paragraph","text":"材料要充分，要做各种各样的准备工作，加强调查研究，做各种人的工作等。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"1fedb79345","type":"paragraph","text":"8、要沉得住气，不要着慌，要稳得住，顶得住。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"31d6eb4fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"9、（因为女儿提出了下乡、下下厂、当兵。）想问题要想得全面，考虑问题要全面，要做当工农兵的准备，也要做掌握印把子、掌握政权的准备，要一颗红心多种准备，以党的需要为第一需要。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d"}],"page":{"id":"72053fd093","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cd25af777d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}